title: SIC! SIC! SIC!

Ristorante 75, N.Y.C., offers “Toastada Italiano—w/ Amaretto Butter Syrup” and “Sankaccino—Sanka, steamed milk & cinnamon.” [Submitted by Dennis Wepman, Bronx.]
